********************* NAS Storage - EFS *********************

- Moderate read / write / file sharing 
- Readymade file system
- FTP / NFS / CIFS(SAMBA)

- AWS not support FTP - it's not secure

- Linux - Unix - Linux --> NFS
- Windows - Linux - Windows --> CIFS

- 8EB

- Regional service - work on VPC

- cnnection 10000 access

#!/bin/bash
yum install -y httpd
yum install -y amazon-efs-utils.noarch
sudo mount -t efs -o tls fs-0fcb778e982a66b61:/ /var/www/html
systemctl enable --now httpd
